51
00:07:13,567 --> 00:07:14,835
<i>-Okay. Are you in danger?</i>

52
00:07:14,936 --> 00:07:18,239
-Hello? Yes, we're being
attacked. Please.

53
00:07:18,339 --> 00:07:20,041
<i>-And what is your name?</i>

54
00:07:20,141 --> 00:07:21,474
