63
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,388
-I need a medic.

64
00:08:40,488 --> 00:08:42,757
-Hang on, girl.
I'm not gonna move you.

65
00:08:42,857 --> 00:08:46,193
Show me where it hurts.
I'm gonna get help.

66
00:08:46,293 --> 00:08:48,429
