203
00:17:52,941 --> 00:17:54,241
-We're hoping.

204
00:17:56,076 --> 00:17:58,813
-Some of the guys chipped in.

205
00:17:58,913 --> 00:18:01,015
Send her love. Okay?

206
00:18:01,114 --> 00:18:04,117
-That's sweet.
Really. Thank you.

207
